thread.title_full: Super Store 4 Less reviewed by William Pinelli

author: William Pinelli
title: William Pinelli
text:
I needed a new manual for my camera and found it thru this seller.
The price was perfect, the manual arrived very fast in a matter or only a few days and the manual was spotless, new, never used.
I could not be happier with my purchase and the service that Super Store 4 Less provided.
I would definitely order more products from them.
